\c 13
\s Ukubusa kukaJehowahazi
\p
\v 1 Ngomnyaka wamatshumi amabili lantathu kaJowashi indodana kaAhaziya inkosi yakoJuda uJehowahazi indodana kaJehu waba yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli eSamariya, \add wabusa\add* iminyaka elitshumi lesikhombisa.
\v 2 Wenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, walandela izono zikaJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati owenza uIsrayeli one, kasukanga kuzo\x + 1 Kho. 14.16.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwaselumvuthela uIsrayeli\x + Hlu. 2.14.\x*, yabanikela esandleni sikaHazayeli inkosi yeSiriya\x + 8.12. 1 Kho. 19.17.\x* lesandleni sikaBenihadadi indodana kaHazayeli\x + 13.24,25.\x*, zonke lezonsuku\x + 13.22. 1 Sam. 18.29.\x*.
\v 4 UJehowahazi wasencenga ubuso beN\nd kosi\nd*, iN\nd kosi\nd* yamuzwa\x + Eks. 32.11. Hlab. 78.34.\x*, ngoba yabona incindezelo kaIsrayeli, ngoba inkosi yeSiriya yabacindezela\x + 14.26. Eks. 3.9.\x*.
\v 5 (IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisipha uIsrayeli\x + 13.25. 14.25,27.\x* umsindisi ukuze baphume ngaphansi kwesandla samaSiriya\x + Hlu. 3.9.\x*; abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebehlala emathenteni abo njengakuqala\x + 2 Sam. 18.17.\x*.
\v 6 Loba kunjalo kabasukanga ezonweni zendlu kaJerobhowamu owenza uIsrayeli one, bahamba kuzo\x + 1 Kho. 14.16.\x*; lesixuku laso sasilokhu siseSamariya\x + 1 Kho. 16.33.\x*.)
\v 7 Ngoba kayimtshiyelanga uJehowahazi abantu, kuphela abagadi bamabhiza abangamatshumi amahlanu, lenqola ezilitshumi, labahamba ngenyawo abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi; ngoba inkosi yeSiriya yayibabhubhisile, yabenza baba njengothuli ngokubhula\x + Amos 1.3.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaJehowahazi, lakho konke akwenzayo, lamandla akhe, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoIsrayeli?
\v 9 UJehowahazi waselala laboyise, bamngcwabela eSamariya; uJowashi indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\s Ukubusa kukaJowashi koIsrayeli
\p
\v 10 Ngomnyaka wamatshumi amathathu lesikhombisa kaJowashi inkosi yakoJuda uJehowashi indodana kaJehowahazi waba yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli eSamariya; \add wabusa\add* iminyaka elitshumi lesithupha.
\v 11 Laye wenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, kasukanga ezonweni zonke zikaJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati owenza uIsrayeli one; wahamba kuzo\x + 1 Kho. 14.16.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaJowashi\x + 14.15.\x*, lakho konke akwenzayo\x + 13.14,19,25.\x*, lamandla akhe alwa ngawo loAmaziya inkosi yakoJuda, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoIsrayeli\x + 14.8-14. 2 Lan. 25.17-24.\x*?
\v 13 UJowashi waselala laboyise, uJerobhowamu wasehlala esihlalweni sakhe sobukhosi. UJowashi wangcwatshelwa eSamariya lamakhosi akoIsrayeli.
\s Ukugula lokufa kukaElisha
\p
\v 14 UElisha wasegula umkhuhlane wakhe afa ngawo\x + 9.1.\x*; uJowashi inkosi yakoIsrayeli wasesehlela kuye, wakhala inyembezi phezu kobuso bakhe, wathi: Baba wami! Baba wami! Nqola yakoIsrayeli lamabhiza ayo\x + 2.12.\x*!
\v 15 UElisha wasesithi kuye: Thatha idandili lemitshoko. Wasezithathela idandili lemitshoko.
\v 16 Wasesithi enkosini yakoIsrayeli: Beka isandla sakho edandilini. Wasesibeka isandla sakhe. UElisha wasebeka izandla zakhe phezu kwezandla zenkosi.
\v 17 Wasesithi: Vula iwindi ngempumalanga. Yasi\add li\add*vula. UElisha wasesithi: Tshoka! Yasitshoka. Wasesithi: Umtshoko wenkululeko yeN\nd kosi\nd*, lomtshoko wenkululeko kuSiriya. Ngoba uzatshaya amaSiriya eAfeki uze u\add wa\add*qede\x + 1 Kho. 20.26. Josh. 12.18.\x*.
\v 18 Wasesithi: Thatha imitshoko. Yasiyithatha. Wasesithi enkosini yakoIsrayeli: Tshaya emhlabathini. Yasitshaya kathathu, yasisima.
\v 19 Umuntu kaNkulunkulu waseyithukuthelela\x + Hlu. 13.6.\x*, wathi: Ngabe utshaye kahlanu kumbe kasithupha, ngakho ubuzayitshaya iSiriya uze uyiqede; khathesi-ke uzatshaya iSiriya kathathu kuphela\x + 13.25.\x*.
\p
\v 20 UElisha wasesifa, basebemngcwaba. Amaviyo amaMowabi asengena elizweni ekuthwaseni komnyaka\x + 1.1. 3.7. 24.2.\x*.
\v 21 Kwasekusithi bengcwaba umuntu, khangela-ke, babona iviyo, baphosela lowomuntu engcwabeni likaElisha. Kwathi umuntu esiyathinta amathambo kaElisha waphila, wasukuma \add wema\add* ngenyawo.
\p
\v 22 UHazayeli inkosi yeSiriya wasecindezela uIsrayeli insuku zonke zikaJehowahazi\x + 8.12.\x*.
\v 23 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisiba lomusa kibo, yaba lesihawu kubo\x + 14.27.\x*, yaphendukela kibo\x + Eks. 2.24,25.\x* ngenxa yesivumelwano sayo loAbrahama, uIsaka, loJakobe, kayithandanga ukubabhubhisa, kayibaxotshanga ebusweni bayo kuze kube khathesi\x + Eks. 32.13.\x*.
\v 24 UHazayeli inkosi yeSiriya wasesifa; uBenihadadi indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 25 UJehowashi indodana kaJehowahazi wasebuya wathatha imizi esandleni sikaBenihadadi indodana kaHazayeli owayeyithethe esandleni sikaJehowahazi uyise ngempi. UJowashi wamtshaya kathathu, waseyibuyisela imizi yakoIsrayeli\x + 13.18,19. Amos 1.4.\x*.